 email        | character varying(255)      |           | not null |         | extended |             |              | 
 phone        | character varying(20)       |           |          |         | extended |             |              | 
 role         | character varying(50)       |           | not null |         | extended |             |              | 
 active       | boolean                     |           | not null |         | plain    |             |              | 
